text: Liam Peters (born 24 January 1997) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mpumalanga in the 2018 Africa T20 Cup on 15 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Mpumalanga cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
